            "title": "警國安處帶走鄭敬基表弟夫婦 返署協助調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄭敬基。鄭敬基IG圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2e96a0038053196b8cbf4ba6d8217a29/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050809294973885.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄭敬基。鄭敬基IG圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警務處國家安全處於去年12月24日公布新一批被國安處通緝名單，包括前無綫藝人鄭敬基等6名竄逃海外人士。消息稱，鄭敬基的57歲姓簡表弟及58歲姓李表弟婦， 於今早（8日）約7時在火炭駿景園家中，被警方國安全帶往警署協助調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4236175/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方懸紅通緝鄭敬基。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa981a4852a99e9845434c50c51f3d5e/2025-05/20240005.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方懸紅通緝鄭敬基。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
